{"tid":675324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣 理解唔到肥人心態","createTime":"2018-05-23T12:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T12:36:42.000Z","uid":79651,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd8caab0d7ede87f80e2b1241f8c8b428e0627c","tid":675324,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"我從來都唔係肥嗰類人，亦唔係啲排骨仔，身材中等。係人都知肥胖對健康唔好，而且肥嘅人郁動唔方便，又唔靈活，除咗脂肪厚啲保暖之外，都無乜優勝之處可言。<br />\n<br />\n我完全忍受唔到自己身形變漲，稍微有個肚腩仔或者肌肉唔夠實，我都頂唔順，要操fit返。究竟點解啲肥仔肥妹忍受到自己啲肉dump吓dump吓咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c093a55134999d46b326e7540dcfd77472fd095","tid":675324,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"49948d1937b24a0e86a862a1453d0593ffd08ccc","tid":675324,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"再嚟"},{"pid":"3ac6543cfc6a9b6b7dde0a0f40812fc828404510","tid":675324,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"有無肥仔肥妹入嚟擺低啲唔運動嘅藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2ae04a1c401cf7ab92dbc29cc8912cb27e746b","tid":675324,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"點解無人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4357a9b75c09536ec6b4b7d073be32381efdd977","tid":675324,"uid":24997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:15:51.000Z","msg":"想肥都肥唔到"},{"pid":"6d667d11ebb0345e2d6ca20e250af6e063ede3eb","tid":675324,"uid":79651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"入嚟擺低你哋唔減肥嘅藉口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />